Added health bar to the slime, added working quest2 and quest3, fixed npc world boundary collision, added diagnol
movement to npc and fixed the resource value issue as stretch goal.
Move player using arrow keys
When you incounter npc press C to chat with him to go to next prompt press enter.
To start the quest press Q near npc to get quest promp and then click yes to start the quest after completing
the quest you can go back to the npc and take a new quest their are a total of 3 quests.
To use bow press E, to shoot left click mouse button, to open inventory press I, to collect apple from tree press E near the tree.
